extendedInfo.description: There comes a point in every man's life where he fantasies about being with a nurse. When you combine a nurturing women in uniform with a nice body, men of all ages find these nurses attractive.Since these women work CRAZY hours, they are limited in finding men outside of the work place. With the dramatic increase of online dating, especially on the mobile side, these women are finding ways to meet men in clever ways. Regardless if you're looking for something serious or a casual thing, nurses can fit the bill in more than one way!This app will explore the various ways that you can meet that nurse! Enjoy
